Subject: drm/vkms: Use drmm_mode_config_init()
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 17e05aeb3b987a17b2ee5185264bec5db1d0c746
